flash.tools.debugger

Interface Isolate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DIsolate, ThreadSafeIsolate

    public interface Isolate
    The Isolate object uniquely identifies a "Worker" in ActionScript. Workers are conceptually similar to Threads, but their implementation closely follows more that of a web worker than an actual OS Thread. By default there is a default isolate object with id DEFAULT_ID.
    Author:
    anirudhs
